data.description:
Beautiful country home for sale by owner sitting on 1/2 acre in Stanton Ky built in 2002.

4 Bdrm 3.5 Bath with 3,500 sq ft
2 Car garage, large 6 bay shed
New Roof 2017, 3 porches/entrances
Gas, electric and city water
Central heat/air

This home features:
Beautiful crown moulding throughout 
Gorgeous Hardwood flooring, carpet and tile
Sunroom, formal living and dining rooms.
Beautiful staircase in front foyer

Too much to list in this amazing home. 
Near mountain parkway, & Red River Gorge.
Less than 1 mile to schools, and grocery.

Call today for showing. You don’t want to miss this!  Call or text 606-481-9536
